    <string name="about_privacy_title">Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="about_privacy_desc">Mo respects and protects your privacy. All data in this app is stored locally on your device. We do not collect, store, or transmit any of your personal information.\n\nData Storage\nAll todo items and memos are saved in the app\'s local database and are never uploaded to any server.\n\nPermissions\n• Notifications: Used only for todo reminders\n• Exact alarms: Used only for scheduled reminders\n• Boot receiver: Used only to restore reminders after reboot\n\nThird-Party Services\nThis app does not integrate any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.\n\nData Export\nYou can back up your data at any time through the export feature. Your data is fully under your control.\n\nContact\nFor privacy-related questions, please contact us via GitHub.</string>
    <string name="about_open_source_title">Open Source Notice</string>
    <string name="about_open_source_full_desc">Mo is Free and Open Source Software released under the MIT License.\n\nMIT License\nCopyright (c) 2025 gascs\n\nPermission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy of this software and associated documentation files (the "Software"), to deal in the Software without restriction, including without limitation the rights to use, copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, sublicense, and/or sell copies of the Software.\n\nThe Software is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind, express or implied.</string>

