    <string name="legal_disclaimer_content">Disclaimer\n\n1. The Mo app is provided "as is" without any express or implied warranties, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.\n\n2. The developer shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from the use or inability to use this app, including but not limited to loss of profits, data loss, or business interruption.\n\n3. The reminder functionality of this app relies on system-level alarm and notification services. Due to deep customizations of Android by different device manufacturers (such as OPPO, Xiaomi, Huawei, etc.), the accuracy of reminders may be affected. The developer shall not be liable for reminder delays or failures caused by system limitations.\n\n4. Users are responsible for their own data backups. Although this app provides export and WebDAV backup features, the developer shall not be liable for data loss.\n\n5. This app may contain links to third-party websites or services. The developer is not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of third-party websites or services.\n\n6. The developer reserves the right to modify or terminate this app at any time without prior notice.\n\n7. By using this app, you agree to all terms of this disclaimer. If you do not agree with any terms of this disclaimer, please stop using this app.</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_content">Terms of Service\n\nWelcome to the Mo app. Please read the following terms of service carefully before using this app.\n\n1. Service Description\nMo is a local todo and memo management app. All features of this app run locally on your device and no online services are provided.\n\n2. Usage Guidelines\nYou agree to use this app only for lawful purposes. You shall not:\n• Use this app for any illegal activities\n• Attempt to reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble this app\n• Copy, modify, or distribute any part of this app\n• Use automated tools to bulk access or operate this app\n\n3. Intellectual Property\nThis app and its original content, features, and functionality are owned by the developer. This app is open source under the MIT License. Please refer to the Open Source License page for specific terms.\n\n4. Disclaimer\nThis app is provided "as is" without any express or implied warranties. See the Disclaimer page for details.\n\n5. Data Security\nThis app stores all data locally on your device. We strongly recommend that you regularly back up your data using the export or WebDAV backup features.\n\n6. Agreement Modifications\nThe developer reserves the right to modify this agreement at any time. Modified agreements will be published within the app. Continued use of this app constitutes your agreement to the modified terms.\n\n7. Contact\nFor any questions or suggestions, please contact us via GitHub:\nhttps://github.com/gascs/Mo-Todo</string>
